'''Majaajilo jaceyl''' waa nooc filim ka mid ah majaajillada iyo sheeko-nololeedka nolosheeda, iyadoo diiradda la saarayo khadadka qalbi furan, kaftanka qosolka leh ee ku saleysan fikradaha jacaylka.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.storyispromise.com/wromance.htm|title=The Art of the Romantic Comedy|last=Johnson|first=Bill|date=|website=|archive-url=https://archive.today/20120910202127/http://www.storyispromise.com/wromance.htm|url-status=dead|archive-date=2012-09-10|access-date=}}</ref> Hal qeexitaan qaamuus waa "filim qosol badan, ciyaar, ama barnaamij telefishan oo ku saabsan sheeko jacayl oo farxad ku dhammaata".<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.macmillandictionary.com/dictionary/american/romantic-comedy|title=romantic comedy (noun) American English definition and synonyms - Macmillan Dictionary|website=www.macmillandictionary.com}}</ref> Qeexid kale ayaa soo jeedinaysa in "astaamaha lagu garto asaasiga ahi uu yahay qorshe jacayl kaas oo laba jacayl oo naxariis iyo wanaag wadaaga ahi ku midoobaan ama ku heshiiyaan".<ref name="depaul.edu">{{cite web|url=http://condor.depaul.edu/dsimpson/tlove/comic-tragic.html|title=Comedy and Tragedy|publisher=}}</ref>

Filimada majaajillada jacaylka ahi waa nooc ka mid ah [[Filimada majaajilo|filimaanta majaajillada]] iyo sidoo kale [[Filimada jaceylka|filimaanta jacaylka]].<ref>Romantic comedy: boy meets girl meets genre. Tamar Jeffers McDonald. Wallflower Press, 2007. p.3</ref><ref name="depaul.edu" />

